    D --> E[Blockchain Integration]
    E --> F[AI Agent Client]
```

## Security Features

PortaSecura includes robust security measures:
- JWT Authentication
- API Key Management
- Rate Limiting
- Input Validation
- CORS Support
- Encrypted Data Storage
- Audit Logging
- DDoS Protection

